line_1: Like NEPTUNE, CAESAR guards VIRGINIAN fleets,
Nor wonder, if Disasters wait your Fleets;
line_2: Nor wonder at Complainings in your Streets:

line_1: While he defends our Isle from hostile Fleets,
line_2: The Fisher undisturb'd at leisure sits;

line_1: Betray'd our Merchants, and expos'd their Fleets,
line_2: And caus'd Eternal Murmurs in our Streets?
